metadata.name: Cat Balloon #1
metadata.description: Cat Balloon is a collection of 3,456 tiny kittens swinging around on balloons! Each Cat starts out with 3 balloons. Selling a Cat will pop 1 balloon and lower chances of getting rare traits! Popping all 3 balloons is Game Over; any Cat sold 4 times over will be instantly burnt. Balloon count determines rarity. The more Balloons you have at reveal, the higher the chances you get a Rare Cat! HANG ON to your Balloons!
